name: Real Jungle Strike Shoot
description:
Real Jungle Strike Shoot is a combination of all the commando and mission based games, you are going to act like an expert cannon, a sniper and a commando at the same time.
- Realistic Graphics
- 3D Environment that gives the real commando feeling
- First Person Shooting
- Excellent city Environment for military attack
- Realistic effects and new challenges to your mission.
- Outclass sound effects, Background and shooting sounds.
